# Crypto Market Feed

A NestJS microservice for streaming cryptocurrency market data.  
It captures real-time market data from various cryptocurrency exchanges and feeds it into Kafka topics for further processing.
This microservice is designed to recreate a high-throughput, low-latency data pipeline for cryptocurrency market data.

## Project setup

Under the hood, this microservice is a NestJS application.

```bash
npm install
```

## Compile and run the project

```bash
npm run start # development

npm run start:dev # watch mode

npm run start:prod # production mode
```

## Run tests

```bash
npm run test # unit tests

npm run test:e2e # e2e tests

npm run test:cov # test coverage
```
